   132	      "PLAN: Choose exactly one next step that best advances the task.",
   133	      "DO: Execute that step using the available tools.",
   134	      "CHECK: Gather concrete evidence and score every criterion honestly:",
   135	      criteria,
   136	      "ACT: Call lykkja_checkpoint with the PLAN, DO summary, and all scores."
   137	    ].join("\n");
   138	  }
   139	
   140	  return [
   141	    "AUTOMATED ACT→PLAN→DO→CHECK PROMPT:",
   142	    `The verdict is ITERATING. Start pass ${s.iterationCount + 1} now, without asking for another prompt.`,
   143	    `PLAN: Fix the weakest failing criterion first: ${s.weakest}. Choose one next step only.`,
   144	    "DO: Execute that step using the available tools.",
   145	    "CHECK: Re-gather evidence and score every criterion honestly:",
   146	    criteria,
   147	    "ACT: Call lykkja_checkpoint again. Continue until the tool returns FINAL or STOPPED."
   148	  ].join("\n");
